:____ g >: ________/: _____/:: Game Notes

What lies hidden in the mysterious walls of Ravenhearst Manor?

The walls of Ravenhearst Manor have been hiding a tragic love story for
over a century. Only the pages of Emma Ravenhearsts diary tell the true
story. Hidden for years, the diary was recently found-only to reveal that
the pages are missing!

Thousands of items are cleverly hidden in the manors 32 rooms. To find
what youre looking for, youll need an unrivalled eye for detail

Door surprises: solve the riddles hidden in these pictures to unlock the
manors secrets

Features:

Thousands of cleverly hidden items to find
Dozens of challenging picture puzzles to solve
Finished? Random item lists ensure a unique experience each time you
play!
